            "segment_id": "seg_008",
            "page_number": 12,
            "section": "great_pillar",
            "speaker": "pixel",
            "speaker_mode": "narration",
            "text": "Not physically—the surface remained solid. But something shifted, a door appearing in Signal-space that only Arc and I could see. He moved toward it, geometric form beginning to fragment, to stream into data.",
            "direction": null,
            "audio_cues": {
                "tone": "transcendent moment, reality bending",
