            "page_number": 12,
            "section": "great_pillar",
            "speaker": "pixel",
            "speaker_mode": "narration",
            "text": "I saw it then—the rush of memories flooding into him. Not just information. Experience. I felt the echo of it through my connection to Arc, through Mochi pressed against me broadcasting what it sensed.",
            "direction": null,
            "audio_cues": {
                "tone": "witnessing arc's experience empathically",
